info.name: Pendle Finance V2 API
info.description:
Pendle Finance V2 API collection for interacting with Pendle's backend services. This includes endpoints for Markets, Assets, Voting, and more.

Base URL: https://api-v2.pendle.finance/core

Rate Limit: 100 points per minute (query costs vary by endpoint)

variable.description: Chain ID - 1 for Ethereum Mainnet, 42161 for Arbitrum, 56 for BSC, 137 for Polygon, 10 for Optimism

request.description:
Returns all active markets on the specified chain.

Example: GET https://api-v2.pendle.finance/core/v1/1/markets/active returns all active markets on Ethereum mainnet.

variable.description: Chain ID - 1 for Ethereum Mainnet, 42161 for Arbitrum, 56 for BSC, 137 for Polygon, 10 for Optimism

Chain ID - 1 for Ethereum Mainnet, 42161 for Arbitrum, 56 for BSC, 137 for Polygon, 10 for Optimism

request.description:
Retrieve historical data for a market in a time-series format.

Example: GET https://api-v2.pendle.finance/core/v1/1/markets/0xe6d4986cd935529fc4505d48e926bcd36a58a0f0/historical-data?time_frame=week

Chain ID - 1 for Ethereum Mainnet, 42161 for Arbitrum, 56 for BSC, 137 for Polygon, 10 for Optimism

request.description:
Retrieve historical data for a market in a time-series format.

Example: GET https://api-v2.pendle.finance/core/v1/1/markets/0xe6d4986cd935529fc4505d48e926bcd36a58a0f0/historical-data?time_frame=week

Retrieve historical data for a market in a time-series format.

Example: GET https://api-v2.pendle.finance/core/v1/1/markets/0xe6d4986cd935529fc4505d48e926bcd36a58a0f0/historical-data?time_frame=week
Retrieve metadata (name, expiry, decimals, address) of all Pendle's assets including LP, YT, PT, and SY tokens.
